729948f-b.title: Richmond: Woodrow Road - Powell Street
729948f-b.text:
1065 Woodrow Road, north side, between 'owell Street
and Lebanon Place (west of Huguenot Avenue), showing the Captsin
I. Cole House. It appears as having Nelonged to the Cole fawily
on the maps from 1853 to 1917.
Spring 1924
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(2)
Another view of the Cole House, seen across Woodrow
Road.
Spriag 1924
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
